00:36:32,225 --> 00:36:34,525
Suýt nữa thì.

676
00:36:38,297 --> 00:36:39,398
Chúa tôi.

677
00:36:39,399 --> 00:36:40,999
Khoan đã.

678
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:43,000
Khốn kiếp.

679
00:36:44,002 --> 00:36:46,937
Khoan. Đừng bảo là
